{"body":"Title: Contribution and Benefit Base. URL Source: https://www.ssa.gov/OACT/COLA/cbb.html. Social Security's Old-Age, Survivors, and Disability Insurance (OASDI) program limits the amount of earnings subject to taxation for a given year. The same annual limit also applies when those earnings are used in a benefit computation. This limit changes each year with changes in the national average wage index. Contribution and benefit base table. Year 2024: $168,600. Note: Amounts for 1978 through 1990 are legislated amounts. All other amounts are determined under automatic adjustment provisions of the Social Security Act.","citation_label":"Contribution and Benefit Base 1","citation_path":"us/guidance/ssa/contribution-and-benefit-base/2024/block-1","document_class":"guidance","expression_date":"2026-07-17","heading":"Contribution and Benefit Base","id":"2d984a6d-9b99-5d76-9988-ae31ec3bdfef","jurisdiction":"us","kind":"block","language":"en","level":2,"metadata":{"block_count":1,"content_type":null,"download_url":"file:///Users/maxghenis/TheAxiomFoundation/ops/1101-migration/us-source-recovery/fetched-round2/ssa-oact-cola-cbb.html","kind":"block","primary_source":true,"source_authority":"Social Security Administration","source_url":"https://www.ssa.gov/OACT/COLA/cbb.html","title":"Contribution and Benefit Base"},"ordinal":1,"parent_citation_path":"us/guidance/ssa/contribution-and-benefit-base/2024","parent_id":"b0b8e3e3-d590-503c-a8e7-fb019579856a","source_as_of":"2026-07-17","source_format":"html","source_id":"ssa-oact-cola-cbb","source_path":"sources/us/guidance/2026-05-26-ssa-contribution-and-benefit-base-2024/official-documents/ssa-oact-cola-cbb.html","source_url":"https://www.ssa.gov/OACT/COLA/cbb.html","version":"2026-05-26-ssa-contribution-and-benefit-base-2024"}
